emerald: Emerald (Compiz Window Decorator)
emerald: 
emerald: The Emerald Window Decorator is a custom window decorator shipped 
emerald: with Compiz Fusion that allows for theming and full composite 
emerald: window decorations with the use of engines. Emerald allows for all 
emerald: sorts of different configurations and layouts of buttons, look, 
emerald: title bars and frames.
